FROM YESTERDAY.

239
00:11:16.910 --> 00:11:19.811
YOU'RE NOT STILL
MAD. ARE YOU?

240
00:11:19.813 --> 00:11:20.745
YEP. HE'S STILL MAD.

241
00:11:20.747 --> 00:11:22.781
(<i> jellyfish buzzing angrily</i> )

242
00:11:22.783 --> 00:11:27.952
(<i> hollering</i> )

243
00:11:27.954 --> 00:11:31.723
(<i> cackling</i> )

244
00:11:31.725 --> 00:11:35.727
(<i> giant jellyfish buzzing</i> )

245
00:11:35.729 --> 00:11:37.562
(<i> stops laughing</i> )

246
00:11:39.399 --> 00:11:41.666
(<i> zap</i> )

247
00:11:42.169 --> 00:11:45.804
(<i> glass shatters</i> )

248
00:11:46.973 --> 00:11:49.074
OW.

249
00:12:01.988 --> 00:12:04.355
Squidward:
ONE CRABBY PATTY FOR TABLE TWO.

250
00:12:04.357 --> 00:12:06.424
SPONGEBOB. I DON'T
HAVE THE WHOLE DAY!

251
00:12:06.426 --> 00:12:09.961
<i>OUI. OUI. UNE CRABBY PATTY.</i>
<i>MONSIEUR.</i>

252
00:12:09.963 --> 00:12:12.330
THERE'S<i> LES PATTY.</i>

253
00:12:14.367 --> 00:12:16.401
COME ON. SPONGEBOB!

254
00:12:16.403 --> 00:12:18.837
NEXT.<i> L'INGREDIENTS.</i>

255
00:12:18.839 --> 00:12:19.938
AH-WHEE!

256
00:12:22.809 --> 00:12:24.642
<i>LES</i> MUSTARD.

257
00:12:25.545 --> 00:12:27.345
WILL YOU QUIT FOOLING AROUND?!

258
00:12:27.347 --> 00:12:28.680
WHERE'S MY CRABBY PATTY?

259
00:12:28.682 --> 00:12:30.882
<i>LES</i> HOLD ON A SECOND.

260
00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:38.656
AND<i> VOILA.</i>

261
00:12:39.126 --> 00:12:40.892
IT'S UNDER
YOUR NOSE!

262
00:12:40.894 --> 00:12:42.527
(<i> cackles</i> )

263
00:12:42.529 --> 00:12:43.828
(<i> laughs</i> )

264
00:12:43.830 --> 00:12:46.231
YOU'RE KILLING ME. SPONGEBOB.

265
00:12:46.233 --> 00:12:47.198
HA. HA!

266
00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.733
YOU REALLY ARE.

267
00:12:48.735 --> 00:12:50.568
SpongeBob:
LOOK AT IT. SQUIDWARD--

268
00:12:50.570 --> 00:12:55.140
MR. KRABS' GIFT TO ALL OF BIKINI
BOTTOM-- THE CRABBY PATTY.

269
00:12:55.142 --> 00:12:57.709
OKAY. GIVE IT TO ME.

270
00:12:59.913 --> 00:13:01.980
COME ON. SPONGEBOB.
STOP IT!

271
00:13:01.982 --> 00:13:04.949
I SWEAR. I'M NOT
DOING ANYTHING.

272
00:13:04.951 --> 00:13:06.184
MR. KRABS!

273
00:13:06.186 --> 00:13:08.453
THAT CRABBY PATTY
IS HAUNTED!

274
00:13:09.456 --> 00:13:11.422
AVAST. YE PATTY PIRATE!

275
00:13:11.424 --> 00:13:13.291
THIS IS NO GHOST.

276
00:13:13.293 --> 00:13:14.893
THIS IS...

277
00:13:14.895 --> 00:13:16.194
PLANKTON!

278
00:13:16.196 --> 00:13:16.961
STEALIN' ME BOOTY!

279
00:13:16.963 --> 00:13:22.167
HEAR ME. KRABS-- WHEN I DISCOVER
YOUR FORMULA FOR CRABBY PATTIES

280
00:13:22.169 --> 00:13:24.569
I'LL RUN YOU OUT OF BUSINESS.

281
00:13:24.571 --> 00:13:27.005
I WENT TO COLLEGE!

282
00:13:27.007 --> 00:13:27.972
HEY!

283
00:13:27.974 --> 00:13:29.574
LET ME GO!

284
00:13:29.576 --> 00:13:32.377
OH. I'LL LET YOU GO.
SQUIRT...

285
00:13:32.379 --> 00:13:34.312
ON A FLYING SAUCER!

286
00:13:34.314 --> 00:13:36.147
(<i> laughs maliciously</i> )

287
00:13:36.149 --> 00:13:39.517
BACK TO THE CHUM BUCKET
WITH YOU!

288
00:13:39.519 --> 00:13:42.654
YOU'LL PAY FOR THIS. KRABS!

289
00:13:42.656 --> 00:13:44.989
UH... PLANKTON. SIR?

290
00:13:44.991 --> 00:13:46.591
AYE. HE'S BEEN TRYING

291
00:13:46.593 --> 00:13:49.093
TO STEAL ME SECRET
FORMULA FOR YEARS.

292
00:13:49.095 --> 00:13:52.363
BUT YE HAVEN'T GOT IT
YET. HAVE YE. BUG?

293
00:13:52.365 --> 00:13:57.035
(<i> both laugh</i> )

294
00:13:57.037 --> 00:13:59.170
(<i> stops laughing</i> )

295
00:13:59.172 --> 00:14:00.205
OKAY.

296
00:14:00.207 --> 00:14:02.540
ENOUGH. LAD.
IT WASN'T<i> THAT</i> FUNNY.

297
00:14:02.542 --> 00:14:05.410
GET BACK TO WORK!

298
00:14:05.812 --> 00:14:08.880
SpongeBob:
OKAY. MR. KRABS.
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

299
00:14:08.882 --> 00:14:11.015
GOOD NIGHT. ME BOY.

300
00:14:16.723 --> 00:14:18.489
Plankton:
PSST...

301
00:14:18.491 --> 00:14:20.325
YOUNG MAN...

302
00:14:20.327 --> 00:14:23.027
YES. OVER HERE.

303
00:14:28.535 --> 00:14:32.003
COME ON. BOY.
A LITTLE CLOSER.

304
00:14:34.107 --> 00:14:36.975
CLOSER.

305
00:14:37.477 --> 00:14:38.910
NOT THAT CLOSE!

306
00:14:38.912 --> 00:14:39.611
AH!

307
00:14:39.613 --> 00:14:42.814
YOU BLASTED BARNICLE HEAD!

308
00:14:42.816 --> 00:14:45.083
I MEAN... HI!

309
00:14:45.085 --> 00:14:46.417
PLANKTON?

310
00:14:46.419 --> 00:14:47.218
OUCH!

311
00:14:47.220 --> 00:14:48.353
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

312
00:14:48.355 --> 00:14:49.854
I JUST WANT TO TALK.

313
00:14:49.856 --> 00:14:52.991
YOU COULD SAY
WE'RE FRIENDS. RIGHT?

314
00:14:52.993 --> 00:14:54.125
UM... NO.

315
00:14:54.127 --> 00:14:55.827
ACQUAINTANCES.

316
00:14:55.829 --> 00:14:56.895
NO.

317
00:14:57.631 --> 00:15:01.065
WELL. WE'RE BOTH INVERTEBRATES.
AREN'T WE?

318
00:15:01.067 --> 00:15:02.100
I... GUESS SO.

319
00:15:02.102 --> 00:15:06.437
YOU SEE. EVERYTHING WORKS OUT.

320
00:15:06.439 --> 00:15:07.839
I HAVE
SOMETHING FOR YOU.

321
00:15:07.841 --> 00:15:11.476
I'VE BEEN KEEPING IT
IN MY SECRET COMPARTMENT.

322
00:15:11.478 --> 00:15:13.478
CHING! SPARKLE. SPARKLE!

323
00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:17.548
WOW! A GOLDEN SPATULA!

324
00:15:17.550 --> 00:15:19.651
AND IT'S EVEN GOT MY NAME ON IT.

325
00:15:19.653 --> 00:15:21.052
IT'S A GIFT.

326
00:15:21.054 --> 00:15:22.687
A GIFT FROM A FRIEND.

327
00:15:22.689 --> 00:15:25.290
FRIENDS GIVE EACH OTHER GIFTS.

328
00:15:25.292 --> 00:15:27.992
AND TOMORROW IS MY BIRTHDAY.

329
00:15:27.994 --> 00:15:29.294
(<i> toots</i> )

330
00:15:29.296 --> 00:15:30.962
AND YOU KNOW WHAT I'D LIKE

331
00:15:30.964 --> 00:15:35.099
MORE THAN ANYTHING
IN THE WHOLE WIDE WORLD?

332
00:15:36.036 --> 00:15:37.035
A BOOSTER SEAT?

333
00:15:37.037 --> 00:15:39.070
BOOSTER SEAT? HOT DOG!

334
00:15:39.072 --> 00:15:40.438
I MEAN. NO.

335
00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:45.410
WHAT I WANT FOR MY BIRTHDAY
FROM YOU. MY FRIEND

336
00:15:45.412 --> 00:15:48.579
IS ONE OF THOSE...

337
00:15:48.581 --> 00:15:51.683
TENDER... DELICIOUS...

338
00:15:51.685 --> 00:15:52.984
CRABBY PATTIES.

339
00:15:52.986 --> 00:15:53.952
(<i> cries out</i> )

340
00:15:53.954 --> 00:15:54.986
YOU JUST WANT
TO BE FRIENDS

341
00:15:54.988 --> 00:15:56.854
SO YOU CAN GET YOUR HANDS
ON A CRABBY PATTY!

342
00:15:56.856 --> 00:15:59.657
AND I BET IT'S
NOT EVEN YOUR
BIRTHDAY TOMORROW!

343
00:15:59.659 --> 00:16:01.960
GEE. AND I THOUGHT
YOU WERE STUPID.

344
00:16:01.962 --> 00:16:05.296
YOU'LL NEVER GET A
CRABBY PATTY FROM ME!

345
00:16:06.366 --> 00:16:07.966
EVEN IF WE ARE FRIENDS!

346
00:16:07.968 --> 00:16:09.901
NEVER. NEVER.
NEVER. NEVER!

347
00:16:09.903 --> 00:16:11.569
OH. I'LL GET A CRABBY PATTY.

348
00:16:11.571 --> 00:16:16.074
AND YOU'RE GOING TO HAND-DELIVER
IT TO ME PERSONALLY!

349
00:16:16.076 --> 00:16:18.977
YOU WEAK-MINDED FOOL!

350
00:16:18.979 --> 00:16:23.147
(<i> dramatic film music plays</i> )

351
00:16:23.683 --> 00:16:25.550
SpongeBob:
NIGHT. GARY.

352
00:16:25.552 --> 00:16:27.185
(<i> meows</i> )

353
00:16:27.187 --> 00:16:29.821
(<i> snoring</i> )

354
00:16:38.264 --> 00:16:40.732
(<i> chuckles</i> )

355
00:16:42.902 --> 00:16:47.705
SPONGEBOB. YOU WILL BE MINE.

356
00:16:47.707 --> 00:16:51.876
Woman:
♪ ...LETTERS OF THE ALPHABET.
A. B. C... ♪

357
00:16:52.512 --> 00:16:58.549
(<i> dramatic film music plays</i> )

358
00:17:02.288 --> 00:17:06.924
IT SHOULD BE IN HERE SOMEWHERE.

359
00:17:07.660 --> 00:17:09.060
BUT WHERE?

360
00:17:09.062 --> 00:17:11.029
WHERE?

361
00:17:11.031 --> 00:17:12.563
OH.

362
00:17:12.565 --> 00:17:15.967
THIS WILL BE THE BEGINNING
OF THE END.

363
00:17:15.969 --> 00:17:20.605
(<i> snoring</i> )

364
00:17:21.574 --> 00:17:23.041
OUCH!

365
00:17:23.043 --> 00:17:24.442
STUPID BRAIN.

366
00:17:24.444 --> 00:17:26.944
COME BACK HERE. YOU SWINE!

367
00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:32.750
WHOA... OOF!

368
00:17:36.823 --> 00:17:39.624
THAT'S IT. BRAIN.
YOU'RE GOING DOWN!

369
00:17:41.895 --> 00:17:43.761
YES. YES. THAT'S GRAND.

370
00:17:43.763 --> 00:17:50.568
AND NOW. FOR MY VERY ELABORATE
AND COLLEGE-EDUCATED PLAN.

371
00:17:54.174 --> 00:17:57.575
AND NOW IT'S TIME
FOR A LITTLE WAKEY-UPPY.

372
00:17:59.846 --> 00:18:02.080
MORNING ALREADY?

373
00:18:07.153 --> 00:18:10.254
I... I FEEL
A LITTLE FUNNY TODAY.

374
00:18:11.825 --> 00:18:14.525
YEAH. YEAH!

375
00:18:20.066 --> 00:18:21.532
I HAVE YOU NOW.

376
00:18:21.534 --> 00:18:24.769
TIME FOR
A WELL-BALANCED BREAKFAST.

377
00:18:25.705 --> 00:18:28.139
THIS ISN'T WHAT I HAD IN MIND.

378
00:18:28.141 --> 00:18:31.008
LET ME JUST GRAB MY PANTS.

379
00:18:31.277 --> 00:18:33.311
I GUESS I'M NOT WEARING
ANY PANTS TODAY.

380
00:18:33.313 --> 00:18:36.848
OOPS! I GUESS I'M NOT
USING THE DOOR. EITHER.

381
00:18:36.850 --> 00:18:39.450
SEE YOU LATER. GARY... I GUESS.

382
00:18:39.452 --> 00:18:40.318
(<i> Gary meows</i> )

383
00:18:40.320 --> 00:18:42.987
YOU'RE RIGHT. GARY. THERE<i> IS</i>
SOMETHING WRONG WITH ME!

384
00:18:42.989 --> 00:18:46.023
SQUIDWARD! SQUIDWARD!

385
00:18:46.025 --> 00:18:49.127
WAKE UP! I NEED SOME HELP!

386
00:18:49.129 --> 00:18:50.795
SQUIDWARD! HELP!

387
00:18:50.797 --> 00:18:53.631
BE QUIET. SPONGEBOB!

388
00:18:54.434 --> 00:18:57.268
HELP!

389
00:18:57.270 --> 00:19:00.338
SPONGEBOB.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

390
00:19:00.340 --> 00:19:02.006
I'M TALKING TO YOU!

391
00:19:02.008 --> 00:19:03.674
SPONGEBOB. SPONGEBOB!

392
00:19:03.676 --> 00:19:05.309
ARE YOU MAD?

393
00:19:06.579 --> 00:19:11.516
(<i> in Plankton's voice</i> ):
SHUT YOUR MOUTH. YOU MEDIOCRE
CLARINET PLAYER.

394
00:19:11.518 --> 00:19:12.950
MEDIOCRE?

395
00:19:12.952 --> 00:19:16.621
YOU PRETENTIOUS LITTLE
INSIGNIFICANT ARTIST.

396
00:19:16.623 --> 00:19:20.024
YOUR SNIVELLY CREATIONS
ARE WORTH LESS

397
00:19:20.026 --> 00:19:21.425
THAN A PROTOZOAN'S WAIST.

398
00:19:21.427 --> 00:19:27.131
(<i> in his own voice</i> ):
SOMETHING MUST BE WRONG
WITH MY BRAIN!

399
00:19:28.101 --> 00:19:29.367
(<i> gasps</i> )

400
00:19:29.369 --> 00:19:30.268
PLANKTON!

401
00:19:30.270 --> 00:19:31.536
WHAT KIND OF
FRIEND ARE YOU?

402
00:19:31.538 --> 00:19:34.272
NONSENSE! YOU NEVER
LIKED ME. ANYWAY.

403
00:19:34.274 --> 00:19:38.176
YOU WOULDN'T EVEN COME
TO MY BIRTHDAY PARTY!

404
00:19:38.178 --> 00:19:39.810
GET OUT OF MY HEAD!

405
00:19:39.812 --> 00:19:41.345
LEAVE MY BRAIN ALONE!

406
00:19:41.347 --> 00:19:44.582
(<i> with Plankton voice</i> ):
NEVER! NEVER!

407
00:19:44.584 --> 00:19:46.150
(<i> laughs evilly</i> )

408
00:19:46.152 --> 00:19:48.252
(<i> sighs</i> )

409
00:19:54.794 --> 00:19:57.161
(<i> snoring</i> )

410
00:19:59.299 --> 00:20:01.032
TOOT. TOOT!

411
00:20:01.034 --> 00:20:03.434
HOW ABOUT A LITTLE TAKEOUT?

412
00:20:03.436 --> 00:20:06.137
SpongeBob:
NOPE. NO. NEVER!

413
00:20:06.139 --> 00:20:09.340
(<i> Plankton laughing evilly</i> )

414
00:20:09.342 --> 00:20:10.741
YOU CAN'T FOOL ME. PLANKTON.

415
00:20:10.743 --> 00:20:12.109
YOU WANT
THE CRABBY PATTY FORMULA!

416
00:20:12.111 --> 00:20:16.547
Plankton:
YOU ARE GOING TO HAND-DELIVER IT
TO ME PERSONALLY.

417
00:20:16.549 --> 00:20:20.151
NO. NO. NO!

418
00:20:20.153 --> 00:20:21.686
THERE'S NO ONE HERE.

419
00:20:21.688 --> 00:20:22.520
DON'T REMIND ME.

420
00:20:22.522 --> 00:20:26.190
Plankton:
BRACE YOURSELF. SPONGEBOB.

421
00:20:26.192 --> 00:20:28.159
THIS IS MY LAB!

422
00:20:28.161 --> 00:20:29.727
(<i> barks</i> )

423
00:20:29.729 --> 00:20:32.263
AND THIS IS MY LABORATORY!

424
00:20:32.265 --> 00:20:36.534
AND DID I EVER SHOW YOU
MY RECORD PLAYER?

425
00:20:36.536 --> 00:20:40.705
(<i> dramatic film music plays</i> )

426
00:20:40.707 --> 00:20:42.273
I MUST FIGHT.

427
00:20:42.275 --> 00:20:44.709
(<i> mumbling nonsensically</i> )

428
00:20:49.148 --> 00:20:51.582
NO. NO. NO. NO!

429
00:20:51.584 --> 00:20:54.819
(<i> screams</i> )

430
00:20:54.821 --> 00:20:55.753
OW. OW. OW. OW!

431
00:20:55.755 --> 00:20:59.857
Plankton:
THERE. YOU SEE
HOW MUCH EASIER IT IS

432
00:20:59.859 --> 00:21:01.559
WHEN YOU HELP. FRIEND?

433
00:21:01.561 --> 00:21:03.494
HOW DO YOU LIKE MY ANALYZER?

434
00:21:03.496 --> 00:21:08.232
IT TELLS THE INGREDIENTS
OF WHATEVER I PUT INTO IT.

435
00:21:08.635 --> 00:21:14.071
Analyzer:
Seaweed: 50% sea. 50% weed.

436
00:21:15.108 --> 00:21:16.240
IMPRESSED?

437
00:21:16.242 --> 00:21:19.710
NOW LET'S REVEAL
THAT SECRET FORMULA.

438
00:21:20.313 --> 00:21:24.348
AND THIS LITTLE PIGGY
BROUGHT HOME A CRABBY PATTY.

439
00:21:24.350 --> 00:21:27.151
THIS LITTLE PIGGY
WILL HELP ME DROP IT IN.

440
00:21:27.153 --> 00:21:30.788
ANY LAST WORDS.
SPONGEBOB SECRETPANTS?

441
00:21:30.790 --> 00:21:33.157
I... I...

442
00:21:34.127 --> 00:21:38.462
I JUST HAVE TO SAY I'M SORRY
I LET MR. KRABS DOWN.

443
00:21:38.464 --> 00:21:40.965
I LET ALL OF BIKINI BOTTOM DOWN.

444
00:21:40.967 --> 00:21:43.301
BUT WORST OF ALL. I LET YOU DOWN

445
00:21:43.303 --> 00:21:46.404
YOU DELICATE LITTLE
CRABBY PATTY.

446
00:21:46.406 --> 00:21:47.271
MMM!

447
00:21:47.273 --> 00:21:50.841
WITH YOUR TASTY.
JUICY. SCRUMPTIOUS

448
00:21:50.843 --> 00:21:53.244
WARM. STEAMY GOODNESS.

449
00:21:53.246 --> 00:21:54.879
STEAMY!

450
00:21:54.881 --> 00:21:59.250
SpongeBob:
I'LL NEVER FORGET
YOUR 100% ALL-SECRET PATTY

451
00:21:59.252 --> 00:22:02.420
SECRETLY ASSEMBLED
WITH UNDERSEA CHEESE

452
00:22:02.422 --> 00:22:05.723
PICKLE. LETTUCE. TOMATO. ONION

453
00:22:05.725 --> 00:22:07.758
ALL SECRETLY STEAMING

454
00:22:07.760 --> 00:22:10.194
BETWEEN TWO FLUFFY
SEAWEED-SEED BUNS.

455
00:22:10.196 --> 00:22:13.831
YES... YES... YES!

456
00:22:13.833 --> 00:22:15.833
COME TO PAPA!

457
00:22:17.403 --> 00:22:18.703
OH. BOY.

458
00:22:18.705 --> 00:22:20.671
(<i> electricity crackles</i> )

459
00:22:20.673 --> 00:22:22.073
(<i> analyzer beeping</i> )

460
00:22:22.075 --> 00:22:27.378
Plankton: One percent evil.
99% hot gas.

461
00:22:29.982 --> 00:22:31.248
WELL. THIS STINKS.

462
00:22:31.250 --> 00:22:34.318
WELL. PATTY. I GUESS
WE CAN GO HOME NOW.

463
00:22:34.320 --> 00:22:39.056
Plankton:
SPONGEBOB. THAT'S
<i>MY</i> CRABBY PATTY!

464
00:22:39.058 --> 00:22:42.626
GIVE IT BACK. YOU POROUS FREAK!

465
00:22:42.628 --> 00:22:44.562
I COMMAND YOU!

466
00:22:44.564 --> 00:22:46.497
MY PATTY!

467
00:22:46.499 --> 00:22:49.166
NO!!!

468
00:22:49.168 --> 00:22:52.169
I'LL SETTLE FOR SOME FRIES.

469
00:22:54.307 --> 00:22:58.209
